title: CPC plans conference to bring together Asian nations on Belt and Road Initiatives
text: The Communist Party of China ( CPC ) hopes that an upcoming conference convening political parties of Asian countries will help draw more consensuses among them on the Belt and Road Initiatives, said a CPC official on Tuesday. Guo Yezhou,
